# ChangeLog for www-client/opera
# Copyright 1999-2009 Gentoo Foundation; Distributed under the GPL v2
# $Header: /var/cvsroot/gentoo-x86/www-client/opera/ChangeLog,v 1.339 2009/05/08 21:03:51 jer Exp $

  08 May 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Version bump
  <http://my.opera.com/desktopteam/blog/2009/05/08/skin-debugging-and-more>.
  Move epatch to src_prepare(). Move opera_cd() into src_unpack() and set S
  only when not set to a valid directory.

  10 Apr 2009; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> opera-9.64.ebuild,
  opera-10.00_pre4205.ebuild, opera-10.00_pre4214.ebuild,
  opera-10.00_pre4268.ebuild:
  Update elog message to reflect package move of net-www/netscape-flash to
  www-plugins/adobe-flash, bug 265569.

  08 Apr 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> opera-10.00_pre4268.ebuild:
  Add late amd64 snapshots (bug #265377).

*opera-10.00_pre4268 (03 Apr 2009)

  03 Apr 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org>
  +files/opera-10.00-pluginpath.patch,
  +files/opera-10.00-pluginpath-fbsd.patch, +opera-10.00_pre4268.ebuild:
  Version bump
  <http://my.opera.com/desktopteam/blog/2009/04/03/turbo-in-10>.

  20 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> opera-9.27.ebuild,
  opera-9.64.ebuild, opera-10.00_pre4205.ebuild, opera-10.00_pre4214.ebuild:
  Define a dummy src_configure, thanks to Rafal Lalik for reporting (bug
  #263010).

  18 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -opera-10.00_pre4166.ebuild:
  Remove old.

  18 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> opera-10.00_pre4205.ebuild:
  Same procedure (bug #227985) so ppc and x86-fbsd users may enjoy this
  enhancement too.

  18 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> opera-9.64.ebuild,
  opera-10.00_pre4214.ebuild:
  DEPEND on x11-libs/qt-3[-immqt] (bug #227985). Either set -immqt or
  +immqt-bc for x11-libs/qt-3 in case of USE="!qt-static qt3(-static)".

  15 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -opera-10.00_pre4102.ebuild,
  -opera-10.00_pre4116.ebuild, -opera-10.00_pre4126.ebuild,
  -opera-10.00_pre4126-r1.ebuild:
  Remove old.

*opera-10.00_pre4214 (13 Mar 2009)

  13 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +opera-10.00_pre4214.ebuild:
  Version bump
  <http://my.opera.com/desktopteam/blog/2009/03/13/opera-turbo-labs-release>
  .

  10 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> opera-10.00_pre4205.ebuild:
  Readd ~ppc. Remove redundant media-libs/libpng dependency.

*opera-10.00_pre4205 (10 Mar 2009)

  10 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +opera-10.00_pre4205.ebuild:
  Version bump
  <http://my.opera.com/desktopteam/blog/2009/03/10/new-peregrine-build>.

  07 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> -opera-9.63.ebuild:
  Remove old.

  07 Mar 2009; Christian Faulhammer <fauli@gentoo.org> opera-9.64.ebuild:
  stable x86, security bug 261032

  04 Mar 2009; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org> opera-9.64.ebuild:
  ppc stable, bug #261032

  04 Mar 2009; Tobias Heinlein <keytoaster@gentoo.org> opera-9.64.ebuild:
  amd64 stable wrt security bug #261032

*opera-9.64 (03 Mar 2009)

  03 Mar 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> opera-9.63.ebuild,
  +opera-9.64.ebuild:
  Version bump (bug #261032). Fix mirrors SRC_URI for version 9.63.

*opera-10.00_pre4166 (12 Feb 2009)

  12 Feb 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +opera-10.00_pre4166.ebuild:
  Version bump <http://my.opera.com/desktopteam/blog/show.dml/2975248>. Drop
  ~ppc because no tar.bz2 has been prepared (yet).

  11 Feb 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org>
  opera-10.00_pre4126-r1.ebuild:
  I can even do spell checking without spellcheck.ini.

  11 Feb 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org>
  opera-10.00_pre4126-r1.ebuild:
  Look mom, I can do spell checking without aspell!

*opera-10.00_pre4126-r1 (11 Feb 2009)

  11 Feb 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org>
  +opera-10.00_pre4126-r1.ebuild:
  Correct spellcheck.so location in spellcheck.ini thanks to MageSlayer (bug
  #258198). Die when spellcheck.so is not found. Refer to LINGUAS for
  >app-text/aspell-0.60.5.

  04 Feb 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> opera-10.00_pre4126.ebuild:
  Depend on media-libs/libpng thanks to Constantine D. Kardaris (bug
  #257437).

*opera-10.00_pre4126 (13 Jan 2009)

  13 Jan 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +opera-10.00_pre4126.ebuild:
  Version bump
  <http://my.opera.com/desktopteam/blog/2009/01/13/new-year-snapshot>.

  30 Dec 2008; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> opera-10.00_pre4116.ebuild:
  Depend on Qt 4 instead of 3 (bug #252630).

