  Depend on app-emulation/emul-linux-x86-qtlibs for amd64 when USE=ia32 (bug
  #227339 comment #5).

  23 Jun 2008; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> opera-9.50-r1.ebuild:
  Change S to reflect USE flag usage (bug #229009, thanks to Branko BAdrljica).

*opera-9.50-r1 (23 Jun 2008)

  23 Jun 2008; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +opera-9.50-r1.ebuild:
  Revision bump to add support for the ia32 USE flag to install a 32-bit Opera
  on AMD64 (bug #227339).

