*opera-9.50_beta2_p1971 (20 May 2008)

  20 May 2008; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> +opera-9.50_beta2_p1971.ebuild:
  Version bump
  <http://my.opera.com/desktopteam/blog/2008/05/20/stability-is-this-weeks-wor
  d>. qt-static defaults to qt4 for now. Qt version support and LINGUAS
  support to be added soon.

